Powered by a 343hp PCM EX 343 engine, this Centurion boat can get you to your favorite spot, or help you discover a new one. Expect clean, rampy wakes for wakeboarding with long transitions and huge landing zones. Surfers should look for Centurion's trademark swell with long pockets, plenty of power and size, and that just-right angle that works well for anything from popping airs on a surf-style board to surface spins on a skim board. From the Gladiator tower to the Clarion head unit with Wet Sounds speakers and the new, zero-learning-curve Micro Touch Screen and with only 73 hours, you will have the peace of mind that comes with a PCM in great condition. Only had 1 owner and it's easy to tell how well she has been cared for. This Centurion boat comes with a BoatMate double axle trailer, included in the price of the boat sale. The SS230 has lots of space for your family and friends, and all your boating gear. This boat boasts a cool CD stereo with rear platform controls (see pic). This boat is in GREAT condition and systems are working well! Priced to sell. See attached NADA appraisal and see just how easy it could be for you too to own an amazing boat like this and financing was super easy through USAA!
title: PRICE LOWERED 2014 Centurion SS230 SURF Boat with ONLY 73 HOURS!!
